### Harm Reduction Disclaimer

The harm reduction resources in this project are for EDUCATIONAL PURPOSES ONLY.
They are NOT medical advice. Always consult qualified healthcare professionals.
If you or someone you know is in crisis, contact:
- SAMHSA Helpline: 1-800-662-4357
- DanceSafe: https://dancesafe.org
- Zendo Project: https://zendoproject.org

In an emergency, call 911 (US) or your local emergency number.

### Experimental Technology Disclaimer

This project uses experimental AI technology including:
- Autonomous AI agents
- AI-generated music and content
- Automated decision-making systems

Use at your own risk. The authors make no guarantees about:
- Accuracy of AI-generated content
- Reliability of autonomous operations
- Fitness for any particular purpose
- Safety of AI-generated music or recommendations

Always review AI-generated content before publishing or performing.
